00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,870
that you promised with your life

293
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:08,230
to the Ministry of Justice in order to investigate this case.

294
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:09,830
You'll be at the disposal of Gongyang Maocai

295
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:11,640
if you can't solve the case.

296
00:14:13,830 --> 00:14:15,000
Don't look at me.

297
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:17,230
I accidentally spilled the beans.

298
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:19,590
How could you promise that

299
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:20,640
to Gongyang Maocai?

300
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:22,160
If he has something on you,

301
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:23,270
he will definitely give you a hard time.

302
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:24,310
Are you crazy?

303
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,870
Mother. Darling.

304
00:14:27,510 --> 00:14:28,770
No need to worry at all.

305
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:30,360
I'm completely confident.

306
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:32,270
Don't worry?

307
00:14:35,830 --> 00:14:37,750
Your life is hanging by a thread.

308
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,430
How can I not be worried?

309
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,440
Mother.

310
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:41,830
I have sufficient evidence

311
00:14:41,830 --> 00:14:43,510
that Lord Chen is wronged.

312
00:14:44,310 --> 00:14:45,390
As the Governor,

313
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:47,160
I can't sit by and watch.

314
00:14:47,310 --> 00:14:48,340
So what?

315
00:14:48,670 --> 00:14:50,350
Countless people are distancing themselves from the affair.

316
00:14:50,350 --> 00:14:51,430
What's the use of taking the risk

317
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:53,760
when your word doesn't carry much weight?

318
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:57,910
I've asked for leave for you from Lord Gu.

319
00:14:57,910 --> 00:15:00,840
From now on, you are not allowed to leave the mansion.

320
00:15:01,470 --> 00:15:02,680
I will ask a favor of Gongyang

321
00:15:02,680 --> 00:15:05,020
for you tomorrow morning.

322
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:05,510
Mother.

323
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,640
It has been decided.

324
00:15:07,430 --> 00:15:08,070
Zhen.

325
00:15:08,470 --> 00:15:09,270
I'm tired.

326
00:15:09,590 --> 00:15:10,790
Take me back to my room.

327
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:11,990
Yes, Mother.

328
00:15:17,310 --> 00:15:17,870
Well,

329
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:20,070
I'll leave if there's nothing else.

330
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:20,910
Stay here.

331
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,250
Since you're here,

332
00:15:24,350 --> 00:15:25,230
have some tea.

333
00:15:31,040 --> 00:15:31,680
Mother.

334
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:33,270
I burned some soothing incense.

335
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:34,220
You may go to bed early.

336
00:15:34,220 --> 00:15:35,150
I'll stay here.

337
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:37,190
Zhen, thank you.

338
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:38,900
Mother.

339
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:41,470
Muchen was impulsive to say that.

340
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:43,270
The worst-case scenario is he will be discharged from the position.

341
00:15:43,270 --> 00:15:45,090
He is intelligent.

342
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:47,270
In addition, I can borrow some money from Jinning.

343
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:49,270
We can live a decent life by running business.

344
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:51,070
Don't be angry about this.

345
00:15:51,790 --> 00:15:53,430
I hope he could be laid off,

346
00:15:53,430 --> 00:15:55,790
so that he wouldn't get himself into trouble.

347
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:56,880
At least it will spare both of us

348
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,670
from worries every day.

349
00:15:59,590 --> 00:16:01,230
If he can't investigate this case clearly,

350
00:16:01,230 --> 00:16:03,670
I'm afraid he won't be able to live in peace for the whole life.

351
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,350
Zhen.

352
00:16:04,660 --> 00:16:06,670
There's something you don't understand.

353
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:09,350
Lord Chen's case is not that simple.

354
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:11,600
Mother, why do you say so?

355
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:15,830
Forget it.

356
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:18,190
Zhen, you may leave now.

357
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:22,630
Okay.

358
00:16:30,190 --> 00:16:37,020
[Memorial Tablet of My Husband, Xu Chengsi]

359
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:49,540
Madam.

360
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:50,630
Madam.

361
00:16:51,990 --> 00:16:53,460
Lord Jiang had an accident

362
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:54,990
and fell down from the cart.

363
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:58,310
What about the other ministers?

364
00:16:58,310 --> 00:17:00,470
They also went to investigate the case of Chengsi.

365
00:17:00,470 --> 00:17:01,510
Lord Wang was framed

366
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:03,080
for colluding with the enemy

367
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,319
and was exiled to the border.

368
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:06,790
Duke Sheng was sent to the Yue State to direct operations.

369
00:17:06,790 --> 00:17:08,550
Now he's trapped in the mountain.

370
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:10,630
The other ministers are in the same situation.

371
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:11,680
Madam, we...

372
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:12,380
Bad news!

373
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,500
Bad news! Bad news!

374
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:14,400
Bad news!

375
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:15,270
Old Madam.

376
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:16,630
Young Master is missing.

377
00:17:16,630 --> 00:17:17,230
Find him.

378
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:18,390
Hurry up.

379
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:19,349
-Yes. -Yes.

380
00:17:23,470 --> 00:17:24,150
Madam.

381
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:25,430
Madam.

382
00:17:47,210 --> 00:17:49,490
Stop it. You are not a good drinker.

383
00:17:50,350 --> 00:17:51,550
It's getting late.

384
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:53,100
Can you let me go?

385
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:53,790
Let me go.

386
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:54,230
Let me go back early.

387
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:55,430
You did it on purpose.

388
00:17:56,270 --> 00:17:57,510
What do you mean?

389
00:17:57,510 --> 00:17:59,310
You deliberately told my mother

390
00:17:59,390 --> 00:18:00,990
my promise to the Ministry of Justice.

391
00:18:00,990 --> 00:18:01,790
How could that be possible?

392
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:02,670
How could I?

393
00:18:02,670 --> 00:18:04,510
How could I say that on purpose?

394
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:06,550
At that time, I was just chatting

395
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:07,910
with Old Madam.

396
00:18:07,910 --> 00:18:08,470
I accidentally

397
00:18:08,470 --> 00:18:09,990
spilled the beans.

398
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:23,550
Don't interfere

399
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:26,330
with Lord Chen's case.

400
00:18:27,390 --> 00:18:28,470
But you know it.

401
00:18:28,470 --> 00:18:29,200
I know it.

402
00:18:31,430 --> 00:18:33,200
Lord Hu lost his life

403
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,550
because of a ledger in Taizhou,

404
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:35,510
while Lord Chen

405
00:18:35,750 --> 00:18:38,750
was imprisoned right after he took office in Taizhou.

406
00:18:40,070 --> 00:18:41,110
Do these things

407
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:44,170
have nothing to do with the flood in Taizhou?

408
00:18:45,190 --> 00:18:45,950
I know

409
00:18:47,190 --> 00:18:48,350
you want to save Lord Chen

410
00:18:48,350 --> 00:18:50,480
for dealing with the flood in Taizhou.

411
00:18:57,830 --> 00:19:00,390
Lord Chen's case should be investigated by the Ministry of Justice.

412
00:19:00,390 --> 00:19:01,870
But you volunteered.

413
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:02,990
Muchen.

414
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:05,480
Can you stop causing this mess?

415
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:07,960
Lord Chen and my father are old friends.

416
00:19:08,710 --> 00:19:10,110
How can I just sit by and do nothing?

417
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:10,910
You are right.

418
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:13,870
But the Zichen Department is an institute of the government.

419
00:19:13,870 --> 00:19:15,330
It's not at your disposal.

420
00:19:17,110 --> 00:19:19,310
If someone has something on you,

421
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,510
you won't be able to

422
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:21,870
explain it easily.

423
00:19:22,470 --> 00:19:23,110
How about this?

424
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:24,640
I'll return this case

425
00:19:24,950 --> 00:19:27,010
to the Ministry of Justice tomorrow.

426
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,630
Do we stop investigating it?

427
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:37,070
It's beyond your duty.

428
00:19:37,590 --> 00:19:38,620
Not only you,

429
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,840
but the whole Zichen Department

430
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,900
can't investigate Lord Chen's case.

431
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:50,600
But this case...

432
00:19:52,870 --> 00:19:54,130
What do you want to say?

433
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:59,190
You are really stupid.

434
00:19:59,870 --> 00:20:01,000
Think about it.

435
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:03,770
What else is there besides the flood in Taizhou?

436
00:20:04,110 --> 00:20:05,270
The Moon Star Herb.

437
00:20:05,990 --> 00:20:07,550
You can go to Taizhou to investigate

438
00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:08,630
in the name of the Moon Star Herb.

439
00:20:08,630 --> 00:20:10,990
You can do whatever you want then.

440
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:13,710
The Zichen Department will fully support you.

441
00:20:13,950 --> 00:20:15,160
Gongyang will have no reason

442
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,660
to interfere.

443
00:20:17,190 --> 00:20:17,990
You are right.

444
00:20:20,530 --> 00:20:21,870
I've offered you the idea.

445
00:20:21,870 --> 00:20:23,730
It depends on you to take actions.

446
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:28,170
But I'm still grounded.

447
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:29,470
Grounded?

448
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:33,360
You want me to

449
00:20:33,360 --> 00:20:35,290
plead for you in front of Old Madam?

450
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:37,960
No problem.

451
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:39,870
But I dare not.

452
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:51,870
Father.

453
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:53,270
What is this?

454
00:20:53,630 --> 00:20:55,250
Lord Chen's testimony.

455
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:56,710
I sent someone to copy it for me

456
00:20:56,710 --> 00:20:58,370
from the Ministry of Justice.

457
00:20:58,470 --> 00:21:00,950
Xu Muchen is investigating

458
00:21:00,950 --> 00:21:02,790
Lord Chen's case.

459
00:21:02,870 --> 00:21:04,950
He wants to clear Lord Chen's name before the case is settled.

460
00:21:04,950 --> 00:21:06,990
He needs this.

461
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:10,230
Besides, Gongyang has a grudge against Xu.

462
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:13,350
There's not enough time

463
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:15,510
to go through all the procedures in the Ministry of Justice.

464
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:16,350
And then?

465
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:19,370
You need to find a way to put it in Xu's Mansion.

466
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:21,880
I'll inform the Ministry of Justice.

467
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:25,040
The Ministry of Justice will search the Xu family.

468
00:21:25,470 --> 00:21:28,630
Xu Muchen will be dismissed and under investigation.

469
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:31,270
Then I'll ask His Majesty

470
00:21:31,630 --> 00:21:33,110
to grant them a divorce.

471
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:37,950
All of this will be reasonable.

472
00:21:38,630 --> 00:21:39,690
Do you understand?

473
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,190
I've considered

474
00:21:52,350 --> 00:21:53,800
everything for you.

475
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,310
As for what to do,

476
00:21:56,760 --> 00:21:58,310
it's up to you.

477
00:22:03,610 --> 00:22:07,410
[Cherish High Aspirations]

478
00:22:37,630 --> 00:22:38,430
Young Master.

479
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:42,230
Have you prepared everything I need?

480
00:22:42,230 --> 00:22:42,990
Young Master.

481
00:22:42,990 --> 00:22:43,630
It's done.

482
00:22:45,390 --> 00:22:45,870
OK.

483
00:22:46,630 --> 00:22:49,480
Invite Miss over for tea.

484
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,090
Yes, Young Master.

485
00:22:56,990 --> 00:22:57,550
Brother.

486
00:22:57,630 --> 00:22:59,190
Why did you invite me here?

487
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:00,830
Nothing.

488
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:02,510
I prepared some desserts.

489
00:23:02,510 --> 00:23:03,560
Have a try.

490
00:23:03,710 --> 00:23:04,350
Have some.

491
00:23:10,590 --> 00:23:11,870
Rong, eat slowly.

492
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:13,490
Tell me which one you like.

493
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:15,270
I'll ask someone to pack some to your residence.

494
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:15,870
No need.

495
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:17,640
I can buy whatever I want.

496
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,390
Although Xu Muchen is not as rich as you,

497
00:23:19,390 --> 00:23:20,830
he can afford desserts.

498
00:23:24,190 --> 00:23:25,230
I heard

499
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:27,470
he got hurt in Pharmacy.

500
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:30,870
There was a fire in Pharmacy.

501
00:23:30,950 --> 00:23:32,030
He went there with his men

502
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:33,350
and fell into the trap of the secret tunnel.

503
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:34,470
If I hadn't saved him,

504
00:23:34,470 --> 00:23:36,000
he would have been dead now.

505
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,360
Did you get hurt?

506
00:23:38,230 --> 00:23:39,390
My head was hit.

507
00:23:39,390 --> 00:23:40,100
Nothing serious.

508
00:23:40,100 --> 00:23:41,350
Your head was hit?

509
00:23:46,110 --> 00:23:47,470
Don't do

510
00:23:47,470 --> 00:23:49,030
such a dangerous thing again.

511
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:51,030
Xu Muchen is not worthy of your care.

512
00:23:51,040 --> 00:23:52,510
Brother, don't say that.

513
00:23:52,630 --> 00:23:53,910
Xu Muchen is my husband.

514
00:23:53,910 --> 00:23:55,150
I can't just let him die.

515
00:23:55,150 --> 00:23:55,680
Husband?

516
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,630
What kind of husband is he?

517
00:23:58,670 --> 00:24:00,390
You should remember that you are a substitute,

518
00:24:00,390 --> 00:24:01,390
not his real wife.

519
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:10,390
Rong.

520
00:24:10,510 --> 00:24:12,310
Do you have feelings for Xu Muchen?

521
00:24:12,310 --> 00:24:13,870
Brother, what are you talking about?

522
00:24:13,870 --> 00:24:15,270
If Master and Senior heard what you said,

523
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:16,870
they would scold me heavily.

524
00:24:17,150 --> 00:24:18,510
So you admit it?

525
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:20,320
I didn't. Don't talk nonsense.

526
00:24:25,390 --> 00:24:26,630
I know what you mean.

527
00:24:26,750 --> 00:24:28,280
You really know what I mean?

528
00:24:32,630 --> 00:24:33,270
Yes.

529
00:24:34,230 --> 00:24:35,230
You are my brother.

530
00:24:35,230 --> 00:24:36,230
You care about me.

531
00:24:42,080 --> 00:24:44,270
Yes, I'm your brother.

532
00:24:46,430 --> 00:24:46,990
Rong.

533
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:49,150
I have something to do today.

534
00:24:49,150 --> 00:24:50,190
I gotta go.

535
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:51,830
Which one do you like?

536
00:24:51,870 --> 00:24:54,530
I'll ask someone to pack some to your residence.

537
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:00,850
By the way, Rong,

538
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:04,470
I was given some toys made in the neighboring country.

539
00:25:04,470 --> 00:25:06,400
I can tell they are what girls like.

540
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:07,590
They are in the back room.

541
00:25:07,590 --> 00:25:08,310
Go pick one.

542
00:25:08,310 --> 00:25:09,370
Take what you like.

543
00:25:09,430 --> 00:25:10,870
Okay, thank you.

544
00:25:15,910 --> 00:25:16,640
Here you are.

545
00:25:17,710 --> 00:25:18,310
Miss.

546
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:19,430
Young Master said

547
00:25:19,430 --> 00:25:22,030
you could pick anything you liked on the table.

548
00:26:05,430 --> 00:26:07,590
Why is there a logo of the Watermill?

549
00:26:08,390 --> 00:26:09,040
Miss.

550
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,520
Have you found the one you like?

551
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,790
I like them all.

552
00:26:15,910 --> 00:26:16,990
Wrap them up

553
00:26:16,990 --> 00:26:18,550
and send them to my residence.

554
00:26:18,550 --> 00:26:19,550
Yes, My Ladyship.

555
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:32,720
[Zichen Department]

556
00:26:35,670 --> 00:26:38,310
Brother Chen was wrongfully imprisoned

557
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:40,430
before he set off to Taizhou.

558
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,230
There must be a backstage manipulator.

559
00:26:43,990 --> 00:26:45,670
It seems that the manipulator

560
00:26:47,230 --> 00:26:48,830
pertaining to the flood case

561
00:26:48,990 --> 00:26:51,350
has done more than corruption.

562
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:53,430
Uncle Liu.

563
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:55,910
An initial investigation of Uncle Chen's case

564
00:26:55,910 --> 00:26:58,000
has been carried out by the Zichen Department.

565
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,130
Please don't worry.

566
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:01,680
Although Uncle Chen is in custody,

567
00:27:02,630 --> 00:27:03,950
he's safe now.

568
00:27:04,590 --> 00:27:06,590
Lord Chen shouldn't have suffered.

569
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,530
I also found some clues

570
00:27:08,550 --> 00:27:11,670
to the case of Hei Limao.

571
00:27:13,120 --> 00:27:16,070
Hei Limao didn't get along well

572
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:18,080
with his younger brother at all.

573
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:20,880
Hei Limao even sold out his younger brother to the government

574
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:23,400
to protect himself.

575
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:27,600
So I think that suicide note

576
00:27:28,240 --> 00:27:31,370
must be a misleading clue by the backstage manipulator.

577
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,350
I found this letter

578
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,810
in Hei Limao's residence.

