00:27:34,690 --> 00:27:38,130
[Kill all the corrupt officials in the world. I'd die without anything to regret after I avenge my brother's death.]

580
00:27:39,670 --> 00:27:40,790
In that case,

581
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:45,350
the backstage manipulator forced Hei Limao to die

582
00:27:47,230 --> 00:27:49,270
to cover up his evil purpose.

583
00:27:50,150 --> 00:27:51,630
So the key to this case

584
00:27:51,990 --> 00:27:53,750
is Lord Hu's ledger.

585
00:27:54,630 --> 00:27:57,440
I have a guess about the ledger.

586
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,740
I'll let you know if there's news.

587
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:03,990
The flood

588
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:05,070
was the trigger of

589
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:08,010
both the cases of the Hu family and Lord Chen.

590
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:10,950
The person behind it is getting more and more unscrupulous.

591
00:28:10,950 --> 00:28:13,000
You must be careful.

592
00:28:14,750 --> 00:28:18,110
Don't let the evildoer take advantage of you.

593
00:28:19,430 --> 00:28:20,630
Thank you, Uncle Liu.

594
00:28:20,910 --> 00:28:21,990
I'll be careful.

595
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:24,430
I will find out the truth

596
00:28:24,540 --> 00:28:26,400
and bring the culprit to justice.

597
00:28:28,410 --> 00:28:30,630
[Xu's Mansion]

598
00:28:51,670 --> 00:28:53,070
Why is there nothing

599
00:28:53,070 --> 00:28:54,670
on the scroll Master gave me?

600
00:28:57,750 --> 00:28:58,710
Who are you?

601
00:28:58,710 --> 00:28:59,710
This is Xu's Mansion.

602
00:28:59,710 --> 00:29:01,630
You can't enter without permission.

603
00:29:01,630 --> 00:29:02,750
He Wei, stop!

604
00:29:05,430 --> 00:29:07,430
The Ministry of Justice is ordered to search here.

605
00:29:07,430 --> 00:29:08,190
Move!

606
00:29:10,390 --> 00:29:12,590
How can the Ministry of Justice hit people?

607
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,310
Apologize!

608
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:15,310
Wu Zhao.

609
00:29:16,710 --> 00:29:18,910
Wu Zhao, forget it.

610
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:21,170
Don't make trouble for Young Master.

611
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:22,470
Apologize!

612
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:25,040
What if I say no?

613
00:29:31,270 --> 00:29:31,910
Wu Zhao.

614
00:29:31,910 --> 00:29:33,440
As a constable of Zichen Department,

615
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,500
how dare you stop the investigation?

616
00:29:37,070 --> 00:29:38,670
Xiao Qiu, step back!

617
00:29:41,870 --> 00:29:42,430
Wu Zhao.

618
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,470
What happened?

619
00:29:48,470 --> 00:29:50,190
Officials from the Ministry of Justice wanted to search the mansion.

620
00:29:50,190 --> 00:29:51,520
They even hurt Xiao Qiu.

621
00:29:54,390 --> 00:29:56,250
Take Xiao Qiu back to the mansion.

622
00:29:56,430 --> 00:29:56,830
My Lord.

623
00:29:56,830 --> 00:29:57,400
Go back.

624
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,590
I don't know why you

625
00:30:09,870 --> 00:30:11,670
broke into my residence at night

626
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:12,790
and hurt my maid.

627
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:13,630
Lord Xu.

628
00:30:13,630 --> 00:30:15,060
The Ministry of Justice received a tip-off

629
00:30:15,060 --> 00:30:17,430
that Lord Xu might have something to do

630
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:19,240
with the missing map of the Ministry of War.

631
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,520
Under the order of the higher-ups,

632
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:22,310
we are here to search your mansion.

633
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:24,110
How dare you search my residence

634
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:26,510
without any solid evidence?

635
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:29,680
Is this how the Ministry of Justice works?

636
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,550
Xu Muchen.

637
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:44,540
The Ministry of Justice is searching for the missing map.

638
00:30:44,790 --> 00:30:46,230
Anyone who stands in the way

639
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:48,670
will be considered as a suspect.

640
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,870
You'd better be sensible.

641
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:54,870
Do you have an order?

642
00:31:07,630 --> 00:31:09,700
I wonder where the Ministry of Justice got the tip-off.

643
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:10,830
It's confidential.

644
00:31:11,230 --> 00:31:12,630
Since you have the order,

645
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:14,310
I dare not disobey.

646
00:31:15,150 --> 00:31:16,870
But you hurt my maid.

647
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:19,270
I will go to the Ministry of Justice to ask for an explanation.

648
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:20,430
If Lord Xu

649
00:31:20,710 --> 00:31:22,840
has nothing to do with the missing map,

650
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:24,550
it's up to you

651
00:31:24,870 --> 00:31:27,470
to go to the Ministry of Justice or not.

652
00:31:27,630 --> 00:31:29,510
But if we find any clue here,

653
00:31:30,070 --> 00:31:30,910
Lord Xu,

654
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:33,400
you have no choice but to go with us.

655
00:31:33,550 --> 00:31:34,110
Search!

656
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:35,280
Yes.

657
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:44,430
Chen.

658
00:31:46,190 --> 00:31:47,250
Search carefully!

659
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,120
Mother.

660
00:31:48,230 --> 00:31:48,870
Chen.

661
00:31:48,990 --> 00:31:50,070
What happened?

662
00:31:50,390 --> 00:31:50,990
Nothing.

663
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:52,790
They probably got a wrong tip-off

664
00:31:52,790 --> 00:31:54,350
so they're here for a routine check.

665
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:55,750
I'll ask them to speed up.

666
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:01,120
Darling.

667
00:32:03,030 --> 00:32:04,750
They kept mentioning a map.

668
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:06,030
What is it?

669
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:09,590
It is a map drawn by every municipal government.

670
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:11,920
It is necessary for military operations.

671
00:32:11,950 --> 00:32:13,790
The map is usually kept by the Ministry of War.

672
00:32:13,790 --> 00:32:15,840
Even three Councilors are not allowed to see it.

673
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:16,970
Anyone who steals it

674
00:32:17,470 --> 00:32:19,000
will be executed according to the law.

675
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,430
Who will be that crazy

676
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:22,950
to steal such an important thing?

677
00:32:23,630 --> 00:32:25,190
The map is priceless and not tradable.

678
00:32:25,190 --> 00:32:27,350
Ordinary gangs won't want it.

679
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:31,110
I guess it was not a thief

680
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:33,260
but a foreign spy who stole it.

681
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:35,830
My Lord.

682
00:32:38,470 --> 00:32:39,730
My Lord, we found this.

683
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,390
Xu Muchen.

684
00:32:54,870 --> 00:32:55,960
What is this?

685
00:32:56,110 --> 00:32:56,870
I don't know.

686
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:58,750
This doesn't belong to me.

687
00:33:07,390 --> 00:33:07,990
Guards!

688
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:09,190
My Lord.

689
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:13,670
This is silverstone powder

690
00:33:13,670 --> 00:33:17,000
designed for decrypting secret letters from the Yue State.

691
00:33:43,870 --> 00:33:44,790
Xu Muchen.

692
00:33:45,910 --> 00:33:47,600
How dare you!

693
00:33:47,750 --> 00:33:48,480
I told you

694
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,070
this didn't belong to me.

695
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:51,730
This is obviously a frame-up.

696
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,080
Mrs. Xu, what's your basis?

697
00:33:57,080 --> 00:33:57,740
Because...

698
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:03,030
Lord Xu is really extraordinary.

699
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:05,630
You know the way to encrypt letters for the Yue State.

700
00:34:05,630 --> 00:34:06,990
I guess you stole the map

701
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:08,909
to claim credit in the Yue State.

702
00:34:10,989 --> 00:34:11,650
Arrest him.

703
00:34:12,110 --> 00:34:12,710
Yes.

704
00:34:19,909 --> 00:34:24,389
[Xu's Mansion]

705
00:34:25,270 --> 00:34:30,250
[Xu's Mansion]

706
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:38,889
[Jinxin Embroidery House]

707
00:34:39,389 --> 00:34:40,110
Master.

708
00:34:40,270 --> 00:34:41,310
I'll buy you some

709
00:34:41,310 --> 00:34:43,150
beautiful hairpins.

710
00:34:47,550 --> 00:34:48,190
Master.

711
00:34:48,270 --> 00:34:49,230
Rong.

712
00:34:49,870 --> 00:34:50,830
What's the matter?

713
00:34:50,830 --> 00:34:51,550
Master.

714
00:34:51,949 --> 00:34:52,989
Why is there a map

715
00:34:52,989 --> 00:34:54,310
in Watermill's box?

716
00:34:55,150 --> 00:34:57,160
What map? What box?

717
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:59,590
It's a box in the Duke's Mansion

718
00:34:59,990 --> 00:35:01,920
with a map of the Jing Dynasty in it.

719
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:03,550
The Watermill hasn't put any box

720
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,430
in the Duke's Mansion.

721
00:35:04,430 --> 00:35:06,230
And I know nothing about the map.

722
00:35:07,350 --> 00:35:08,210
Who could it be?

723
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,020
Have a seat.

724
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:15,840
What on earth happened?

725
00:35:16,150 --> 00:35:17,390
I found a box

726
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:18,470
at Jinning's residence.

727
00:35:18,470 --> 00:35:19,910
There was a logo of the Watermill on it

728
00:35:19,910 --> 00:35:21,510
and a blank scroll inside.

729
00:35:22,350 --> 00:35:24,550
I thought it was a new task from Master,

730
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:25,520
so I took it back.

731
00:35:26,030 --> 00:35:27,430
But why did the Ministry of Justice

732
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:29,030
come to search Xu's Mansion?

733
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:30,780
And how could they know that the blank scroll

734
00:35:30,780 --> 00:35:33,640
was the map of the Jing Dynasty drawn in a secret way?

735
00:35:36,790 --> 00:35:38,760
The map is related to the spy of Yue.

736
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:40,470
They arrested Xu Muchen

737
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:41,730
in the name of treason.

738
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,430
So you think

739
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:45,760
Xu Muchen was framed by the Watermill?

740
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,650
I dare not to doubt that.

741
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:49,990
I'm sure the Watermill won't collude with the Yue State.

742
00:35:49,990 --> 00:35:52,470
There's no reason for the Watermill to frame Xu Muchen.

743
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:53,310
But...

744
00:35:54,590 --> 00:35:56,200
Are we being used?

745
00:35:56,710 --> 00:35:57,440
How dare you!

746
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:02,470
Rong.

747
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:05,630
Why are you so anxious

748
00:36:06,870 --> 00:36:08,830
that Xu Muchen was arrested?

749
00:36:10,790 --> 00:36:11,600
Because...

750
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,910
Because I haven't found the jade pendant yet.

751
00:36:14,910 --> 00:36:15,960
If he gets caught,

752
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:18,750
I won't be able to complete the task you assigned to me.

753
00:36:18,750 --> 00:36:20,560
Now you want to finish the task?

754
00:36:20,910 --> 00:36:22,270
Why don't you finish it earlier?

755
00:36:22,270 --> 00:36:23,400
Don't be sarcastic.

756
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:24,710
Stop it!

757
00:36:34,370 --> 00:36:35,630
I promise you

758
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:38,310
the Watermill has nothing to do

759
00:36:38,310 --> 00:36:39,590
with the map.

760
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:44,230
Rong.

761
00:36:44,950 --> 00:36:47,070
Don't forget who you really are.

762
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:49,360
You're not Su Jinzhen.

763
00:36:49,430 --> 00:36:51,830
Your marriage is just an expedient.

764
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:54,210
You need to come back sooner or later.

765
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:56,310
Don't fall in love with him.

766
00:37:00,740 --> 00:37:04,810
[Vigor and High Spirits]

767
00:37:03,270 --> 00:37:03,790
Rong.

768
00:37:03,790 --> 00:37:04,950
Come here and have a seat.

769
00:37:04,950 --> 00:37:05,870
What happened?

770
00:37:05,870 --> 00:37:07,000
Anyone bullied you?

771
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,440
Xu Muchen was arrested.

772
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,470
Finally.

773
00:37:12,710 --> 00:37:14,640
I knew he would be arrested one day.

774
00:37:16,950 --> 00:37:17,950
What did he do?

775
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:19,800
It's my fault.

776
00:37:21,350 --> 00:37:22,320
Who put the box of the Watermill

777
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:24,470
in your room yesterday?

778
00:37:27,430 --> 00:37:29,810
Why was there a box of the Watermill

779
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,620
in my room?

780
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:41,880
[Vigor and High Spirits]

781
00:37:31,830 --> 00:37:33,150
I don't know.

782
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:33,950
But Master said

783
00:37:33,950 --> 00:37:36,230
the box didn't belong to the Watermill.

784
00:37:36,950 --> 00:37:38,470
Then who put it?

785
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:42,040
Let me ask you.

786
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:44,110
Did you see anyone

787
00:37:44,110 --> 00:37:46,310
put anything in the mansion yesterday?

788
00:37:49,310 --> 00:37:50,110
Young Master.

789
00:37:50,310 --> 00:37:52,470
No outsider came here yesterday.

790
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,790
I see. You may leave.

791
00:37:56,110 --> 00:37:57,170
Yes, Young Master.

792
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:00,790
Rong.

793
00:38:02,110 --> 00:38:03,950
If someone is good at martial arts like you

794
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:04,910
who can fly over the eaves

795
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:05,910
and walk on walls,

796
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:08,070
I don't think my servants

797
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:09,270
can notice him.

798
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:12,350
Who is trying to frame Xu Muchen?

799
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:15,680
Rong.

800
00:38:15,940 --> 00:38:18,670
It's a good thing that Xu Muchen is arrested and imprisoned.

801
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:19,630
We can take this opportunity

802
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,670
to divorce him.

803
00:38:20,790 --> 00:38:21,780
It's justifiable.

804
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:23,110
It won't ruin Zhen's reputation either.

805
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:24,030
No.

806
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:26,840
It was my fault.

807
00:38:26,990 --> 00:38:28,670
I can't leave him alone now.

808
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,400
What are you going to do?

809
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,380
I must save him.

810
00:38:45,090 --> 00:38:46,150
-My Lord. -My Lord.

811
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:47,750
My Lord.

812
00:38:48,470 --> 00:38:51,310
Your father committed corruption,

813
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:52,990
while you

814
00:38:53,270 --> 00:38:55,870
dare to collude with the enemy and betray the country.

815
00:38:55,870 --> 00:38:56,670
Lord Xu.

816
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:59,190
You are more audacious than your father.

817
00:38:59,190 --> 00:39:00,350
Nonsense!

818
00:39:01,790 --> 00:39:03,520
The map is our military secret.

819
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:05,280
It's the key to the deployment.

820
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:06,910
Once it falls into the hands of the enemies,

821
00:39:06,910 --> 00:39:08,150
our landscape

822
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:08,950
will be exposed

823
00:39:08,950 --> 00:39:10,350
to them completely.

824
00:39:10,470 --> 00:39:11,750
At that time,

825
00:39:11,950 --> 00:39:13,830
the opponents will know every move we are going to make,

826
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:14,670
while we

827
00:39:14,870 --> 00:39:16,400
will be like their prey.

828
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:19,190
Now Lord Xu planned to give the map to the Yue State.

829
00:39:19,190 --> 00:39:22,430
Does that mean you want to give the whole country to them?

830
00:39:26,280 --> 00:39:27,260
Lord Gongyang.

831
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:30,630
You're really silly.

832
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:34,630
You can't even notice this is a frame-up?

833
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,620
The evidence is solid.

834
00:39:37,630 --> 00:39:40,760
It won't work even if you try to deny it.

835
00:40:00,400 --> 00:40:05,880
[Diligence Hall]

836
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:10,830
[Diligence Hall]

837
00:40:11,270 --> 00:40:12,590
What did His Majesty say?

838
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:14,750
Lord Xu is suspected of treason.

839
00:40:14,800 --> 00:40:15,910
It's extremely serious.

840
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:17,120
His Majesty has made it clear

841
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,950
that the case must be investigated thoroughly.

842
00:40:18,950 --> 00:40:21,350
The Ministry of Justice has been in charge.

843
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,310
Princess.

844
00:40:23,270 --> 00:40:24,710
Please leave here.

845
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:26,790
I believe His Majesty

846
00:40:26,790 --> 00:40:28,270
will clear my son's name.

847
00:40:28,630 --> 00:40:30,950
But my son has been framed and imprisoned.

848
00:40:30,950 --> 00:40:32,740
I'm really worried.

849
00:40:35,270 --> 00:40:35,910
Sir.

850
00:40:36,870 --> 00:40:39,110
Please ask a favor of His Majesty for me.

851
00:40:39,230 --> 00:40:40,470
Let me see Muchen.

852
00:40:43,870 --> 00:40:45,460
[Diligence Hall]

853
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,590
How could Young Master give the map

854
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:53,880
to the Yue State?

855
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:56,500
Who is trying to frame Young Master?

856
00:40:57,270 --> 00:40:58,830
What should we do now?

857
00:40:58,830 --> 00:41:01,080
If Young Master is convicted of treason,

858
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:03,980
he'll have no chance to survive.

859
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:06,540
Xiao Qiu, stop crying.

860
00:41:06,770 --> 00:41:08,900
I feel even more upset when you cry.

861
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:14,150
Mother.

